OL,3,CFour teens drown over Bank Holiday
OL,4,Cweekend amid record-breaking May heat
OL,6,FFour teenagers drowned in separate
OL,7,Fopen water incidents over the Bank
OL,8,FHoliday weekend amid record-breaking
OL,9,Ftemperatures across the UK.
OL,11,FThree teen boys and one girl died
OL,12,Fafter going into the water in
OL,13,FLincolnshire, South Yorkshire, West
OL,14,FYorkshire, and Warwickshire, police
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FReco Pinnock, 13, was pronounced dead
OL,18,Fin hospital after he was pulled from a
OL,19,Freservoir at Leadbeater Dam, Halifax,
OL,20,Fjust after 3pm on Monday, West
OL,21,FYorkshire Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
