OL,3,CFour teens drown over Bank Holiday
OL,4,Cweekend amid record-breaking May heat
OL,6,FCalderdale CID are investigating the
OL,7,Fdeath, but it is not believed to be
OL,8,Fsuspicious.
OL,10,FHours later, the body of a teenage
OL,11,Fgirl was recovered from Kingsbury
OL,12,FWater Park, just south of Tamworth,
OL,13,FStaffordshire, on Monday evening
OL,14,Ffollowing a police search.
