OL,3,CFour teens drown over Bank Holiday
OL,4,Cweekend amid record-breaking May heat
OL,6,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,7,Fservices, she was pronounced dead at
OL,8,Fthe scene, Atherstone and Coleshill
OL,9,FPolice said.
OL,11,FThe body of another boy was found at
OL,12,FRother Valley Country Park during the
OL,13,Fearly hours of Tuesday morning,
OL,14,Ffollowing reports of a missing child
OL,15,Fseen entering the water but not
OL,16,Fgetting out.
