OL,3,CFour teens drown over Bank Holiday
OL,4,Cweekend amid record-breaking May heat
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService and the Yorkshire Ambulance
OL,8,FService had launched a specialist
OL,9,Fsearch operation shortly before 7pm on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,FFormal identification has not been
OL,13,Fconfirmed, but the the boy's family
OL,14,Fhas been informed, police said.
OL,16,FThe incidents follow the death of 15-
OL,17,Fyear-old Declan Sawyer, whose body was
OL,18,Ffound in a Lincoln lake on Sunday
OL,19,Faround 10.25pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
