OL,3,CFour teens drown over Bank Holiday
OL,4,Cweekend amid record-breaking May heat
OL,6,FDeclan's father Carl described him as
OL,7,F"a funny and outgoing young man who
OL,8,Floved fishing and football" as he
OL,9,Fcalled on families to take care of
OL,10,Ftheir children when near water.
OL,12,F"He had a very cheeky smile and the
OL,13,Fpersonality to match. He was very much
OL,14,Floved by his friends and family, and
OL,15,Fwill be missed dearly by many," Carl
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"Please can all parents, friends and
OL,19,Ffamily make their children aware of
OL,20,Fthe dangers surrounding water."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
