OL,3,CFour teens drown over Bank Holiday
OL,4,Cweekend amid record-breaking May heat
OL,6,FA man in his 60s also died at Tregirls
OL,7,FBeach, near Padstow, on Monday after
OL,8,Fsuffering a a cardiac arrest in the
OL,9,Fsea while trying to help family
OL,10,Fmembers who had got into difficult in
OL,11,Fthe water, Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe relatives were brought to shore by
OL,15,Fmembers of the public during the
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,FThe UK recorded its hottest ever May
OL,19,Ftemperature on Bank Holiday Monday -
OL,20,Fbreaking a record set just one day
OL,21,Fearlier on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
